reviews.review_text:
Wish I was a Headlight! I think most would agree that a good China>Rider is all about the transition jam, and then the "Wish I was a Headlight" line... transition is nice enough here, but the Headlight, well check it out for yourselves... BOOM! 

Could it be one of THE all time Headlights?

More crunchy '85 stuff always welcome and appreciated from Charlie & Co. Cheers guys!
